diff --git a/README.md b/README.md
index 27c870e..4e7de3c 100644
--- a/README.md
+++ b/README.md
@@ -169,3 +169,13 @@ Step 6f.0.4 completion safeguards migration complete
 - Approved assignment transfer and any approved lot move occur together and create assignment and lot-move history records.
 - Parent/container lots remain non-assignable; an old unit currently in a parent lot requires an assignable destination selection during a recorded-work override.
 - No SQL migration is required.
+
+## Step 6f.0.4e — Personal Earned-Weight Placement and Privacy
+
+- Keeps the Unit Browser row focused on the current **Assigned To** value only.
+- Removes Last Credited Tech and earned-weight values from the row.
+- Adds a lazy-loaded **My Weight Earned** panel inside the expanded Unit Details mini-menu for regular Tech users.
+- The personal panel returns only the signed-in Tech's own recorded work-credit entries for that unit.
+- Admin, Management, and Tech Lead continue to use the separate lazy-loaded **History** panel for full earned-weight history and other audit records.
+- Removes the unneeded latest-completion lookup from the main Unit Browser render path.
+- No SQL migration is required.
